---
By: Mother Teresa
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 153
    Verse: 11
Tags:
  - Faith
---
If faith is lacking, it is because there is too much selfishness, too much
concern for personal gain. For faith to be true, it has to be generous and
loving. Love and faith go together, they complete each other.
